import React from 'react'

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <SidebarContainer>
            <Icon >
                <CloseIcon />
            </Icon>
            <SidebarMenu>
               
                <SidebarLink to='/'>Pizzas</SidebarLink>
                <SidebarLink to='/'>Desserts</SidebarLink>
                <sidebarLink to='/'>Full Menu</sidebarLink>
            </SidebarMenu>
            <SideBtnWrap>
                <SidebarRoute to='/'>Order Now</SidebarRoute>
            </SideBtnWrap>
        </SidebarContainer>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
